  "description": "<p>当你正在某个风景宜人的地方喝着鸡尾酒、跟旅友讨论周边风土人情的时候，相信会非常不乐意接到任何跟工作相关的短信、电话、邮件等。但是，随着科学技术的发展，人们似乎已经很难逃脱出这个无形的魔爪。<strong>据TeamViewer最新发布的报告显示，今年，有61%的美国人都表示自己会在度假期间接到工作相关的通知，这个数字要比上一年高出9个百分点。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eb5b8ce/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244855.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A61%25%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244855.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A61%25%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244855.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A61%25%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244855.htm&amp;t=%E8%B0%83%E6%9F%A5%EF%BC%9A61%25%E7%9A%84%E7%BE%8E%E5%9B%BD%E4%BA%BA%E4%BC%9A%E5%9C%A8%E5%BA%A6%E5%81%87%E6%9C%9F%E9%97%B4%E6%8E%A5%E5%88%B0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Fartic