  "description": "<p><strong>Google已在今天对其Play商店的Web界面进行了改版。新版本从今天起面向所有人开放，并且把Android版本带到了Web上。</strong>有了这个新的设计，用户能够更容易地了解某个应用。更重要的是，如果你注意到一个应用的细节的话，会发现截图也更大了。在商店中，用户将能够在单页里看到满屏的信息——不再有那些让人凌乱的标签页。<br /></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2eb5b8cd/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244854.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%B5%93%E6%B5%93Android%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%9AWeb%E7%89%88Play%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%94%B9%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244854.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%B5%93%E6%B5%93Android%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%9AWeb%E7%89%88Play%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%94%B9%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244854.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%B5%93%E6%B5%93Android%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%9AWeb%E7%89%88Play%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%94%B9%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244854.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%B5%93%E6%B5%93Android%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%9AWeb%E7%89%88Play%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E5%85%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%94%B9%E7%89%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/email/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F244854.htm&amp;t=%5B%E5%9B%BE%5D%E6%B5%93%E6%B5%93Android%E9%A3%8E%EF%BC%9AWeb%E7%89%88Play%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97%E5%8